  <span id="freeText1686084465823843456" style="display:none">I have many thoughts about this book, but can summarize in one word, “disappointing”. <br /><br />I had to put the book down so many times after reading many paragraphs that made me question the validity of the author’s statements. There was no evidence behind many of the information that was shared and the arguments were very weak. <br /><br />Overall, the book was easy to read and follow. The author did a good job simplifying religious concepts, however, my biggest concern is the content. Specially when it comes to religious content, it has to be research based and well vetted, and no one should be spreading misleading or questionable information. The book left me with more questions than answers. I don’t recommend the book.</span>
