<span id="freeTextContainer10806779417213461129">To be quite honest, the book did not amaze me. Yet I can&apos;t say it wasn&apos;t good or helpful. It was a nice research and information gathering by a a moderately good author who wanted nothing but to share his passion towards these things with people. It&apos;s not his problem if you don&apos;t share his point of views. In fact, it&apos;s no-one&apos;s problem. The burden lays on you to see for yourself if what he mentioned is useable in everyday arguments.</span>
  <span id="freeText10806779417213461129" style="display:none">To be quite honest, the book did not amaze me. Yet I can't say it wasn't good or helpful. It was a nice research and information gathering by a a moderately good author who wanted nothing but to share his passion towards these things with people. It's not his problem if you don't share his point of views. In fact, it's no-one's problem. The burden lays on you to see for yourself if what he mentioned is useable in everyday arguments.</span>
